# 5. Advantages and Limitations of JavaScript

# Advantages of JavaScript

---

## 1. Easy to Learn

JavaScript syntax is simple and beginner-friendly.

---

## 2. Fast Execution

Runs directly in the browser.

---

## 3. Platform Independent

Works on all major operating systems.

---

## 4. Large Community Support

Millions of developers use JavaScript.

---

## 5. Rich Ecosystem

Thousands of libraries and frameworks are available.

---

## 6. Supports Both Frontend and Backend

JavaScript can be used for full-stack development.

