---

# Limitations of JavaScript

---

## 1. Security Risks

JavaScript code is visible in browsers.

---

## 2. Browser Compatibility Issues

Some features may work differently in different browsers.

---

## 3. Single-Threaded

JavaScript executes one task at a time.

---

## 4. Debugging Complexity

Large applications can become difficult to debug.

---

## 5. Limited File Access

Browsers restrict access to local files for security.

