# 12. Type Conversion

## Definition

Type conversion means converting one datatype into another.

---

# Types of Conversion

## 1. Implicit Conversion

Automatically done by JavaScript.

```javascript
let result = "5" + 2;
```

Output:

```javascript
52
```

---

## 2. Explicit Conversion

Manually done by programmer.

### String to Number

```javascript
Number("10");
```

### Number to String

```javascript
String(100);
```

### Boolean Conversion

```javascript
Boolean(1);
```

